<br>
If you have enough mana to blast every mob from 30% to dead, even velious mobs, then you're doing great.  Aggro won't be an issue, because the beast lays in a smoking heap of ashes.<br>
<br>
Combine this with total fix / removal of spell resists, mana regen and (possibly) larger mana pool and you've got wizards who dish out damage like a warrior.<br>
